Package chessai.chessai.lib

Record Class MoveResult

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
chessai.chessai.lib.MoveResult
Record Components:
moveTargets - the squares, this piece can move to
isResultCapture - the squares, this piece can capture
attackTargetsWhilePretendingTheEnemyKingIsNotThere - the squares that this piece can attack (had the enemy king not been there)
isResultPromotion - the squares, onto which a move would result in a promotion
isResultEnPassant - the squares, onto which a move would result in an en passant
isResultDoublePawnMove - the squares, onto which a move would result in a double pawn push
isResultKingSideCastle - the squares, onto which a move would result in a king side castle
isResultQueenSideCastle - the squares, onto which a move would result in a queen side castle
pinMap - the piece, this piece pins
checkTrack - the track of the check this piece causes
isEnPassantTargetUnCapturableBecausePin - the squares that are uncapturable en passant targets
public record MoveResult(BitMap moveTargets, BitMap isResultCapture, BitMap attackTargetsWhilePretendingTheEnemyKingIsNotThere, BitMap isResultPromotion, BitMap isResultEnPassant, BitMap isResultDoublePawnMove, BitMap isResultKingSideCastle, BitMap isResultQueenSideCastle, BitMap pinMap, BitMap checkTrack, BitMap isEnPassantTargetUnCapturableBecausePin) extends Record
This is a helper class that is returned by the piece when generating the pseudo legal moves.
